# Very small README for xneur keyboard auto-switcher 

1. Read documentation at http://dists.xneur.ru/

2. Check /etc/xneur/xneurrc configuration file. 
Now activated English/Russian auto-switch only for next applications: 
Abiword, Gnumeric, Firefox, Thunderbird, Licq. In other app. auto-switch 
keyboard are disable. Sounds are also disabled. For undo chacking of inputted 
words use Break.

3. Add /usr/bin/xneur to startup with your WM.

4. That's all.
